    "description": "<strong>Annihilate an endless horde of monsters with the ultimate spell builder!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163400/extras/a062d21be8f128de3c9987a7fc4a4b03.poster.avif?t=1695753409\" width=524 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163400/extras/a062d21be8f128de3c9987a7fc4a4b03.webm?t=1695753409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163400/extras/a062d21be8f128de3c9987a7fc4a4b03.mp4?t=1695753409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In this action roguelite game, harness the power of the ultimate spell crafting system to create weapons beyond your wildest dreams and wreak havoc against the monsters seeking your destruction. Utilize an arsenal of mods to customize a spell type and unleash it upon the monsters. With a fully modular spell builder, no run is quite like another, and the possibilities are limited only by your imagination (and your computer hardware).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163400/extras/40c5fd8a18d01414226ae219ca571f14.poster.avif?t=1695753409\" width=524 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163400/extras/40c5fd8a18d01414226ae219ca571f14.webm?t=1695753409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163400/extras/40c5fd8a18d01414226ae219ca571f14.mp4?t=1695753409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163400/extras/cdb69647f7958ce485c4fcec78d0948a.poster.avif?t=1695753409\" width=524 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163400/extras/cdb69647f7958ce485c4fcec78d0948a.webm?t=1695753409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163400/extras/cdb69647f7958ce485c4fcec78d0948a.mp4?t=1695753409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- A powerful spellbuilder with a focus on modularity and freedom<br>- Forbidden Magics with tremendous power but potentially deadly consequences<br>- Equippable items to enhance the player's speed and power<br>- A progression system to become stronger every run<br>- Challenging bosses with unique mechanics to push your spell building to the limit<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163400/extras/5117c1dd9c31e74108fc0973df153376.poster.avif?t=1695753409\" width=524 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163400/extras/5117c1dd9c31e74108fc0973df153376.webm?t=1695753409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163400/extras/5117c1dd9c31e74108fc0973df153376.mp4?t=1695753409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
